    <detaileddescription>
<para>A lightweight, formattable view over a range that renders its elements separated by a delimiter.</para>
<para>This is a drop-in replacement for <computeroutput>fmt::join</computeroutput>, which has no equivalent in <computeroutput>std::format</computeroutput> (C++20). It allocates nothing of its own: elements are written straight to the output iterator. </para>
